mistral.reason: "Because You Are Here" is not the note of the entire music of Final Fantasy XIII. It is one of the theme songs, specifically the theme song of the Japanese version, and not a representative of the entire soundtrack which consists of various tracks.

gemma2.reason: Several passages mention "Because You're Here" as the theme song for the *Japanese* version of Final Fantasy XIII, and a separate English theme song by Leona Lewis titled "My Hands" was used. It doesn't establish this as the overarching musical note for the entire soundtrack.

qwen2.5.reason: "Because You're Here" is the theme song for the Japanese version of Final Fantasy XIII, not a note from the game's soundtrack.
